item.title: Little Help
item.dc:creator: @lothy Lothy
item.description:
@lothy wrote:

[quote=“l Whitney l, post:1, topic:58277”]When i Rune The Runserver.bat Says connecting to server 0.0.0.0:43594

How can i cange that to the no-ip host i made?[/quote]
You don’t need to. It shows the address of the server in respect to you - You don’t access it with the no-ip, you access it, in most cases, 127.0.0.1 or localhost - That’s just another local address you can use to access it.

In other words, ignore it, it’s irrelevant.
